  summary: Not a channeler, but part of the same social cluster. Often helps conversation
    drift in unexpected directions.
  cues:
  - CueId: greeting
    TriggerKeyword: 
    Line: I was following Marie, then a bird, then maybe a rumor?
    JournalNote: Amy drifts into useful information by accident.
    QuestToStart: {fileID: 0}
    Importance: 0
  - CueId: rumor
    TriggerKeyword: rumor
    Line: Someone said something important. I remember because I forgot why it mattered.
    JournalNote: Amy can accidentally surface clues.
    QuestToStart: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 0bec97312f68173438b9262135da8037, type: 2}
    Importance: 1
  - CueId: friends
    TriggerKeyword: friends
    Line: I just go where everyone else goes. It usually becomes interesting.
    JournalNote: Amy keeps the social group moving.
    QuestToStart: {fileID: 0}
    Importance: 0
